The original Humphrey's East located at the corner of Humphrey and East streets in New Haven opened in 1984. The "neighborhood original" is best known for award winning wings and Happy Hour. You can also find the "Best Sandwiches" as voted by Connecticut Magazine, along with mouth watering burgers and some of best live bands. If you like outstanding food, good people and great music, come to New Haven’s favorite neighborhood bar & grill, at Humphrey’s East Restaurant…family dining at its best.
